:72.2,"long_business_summary":"Meta Infotech Limited provides cybersecurity solutions to various organizations in India. It offers secure access service edge solutions, including software-defined wide area network, cloud access security broker, secure web gateway, zero trust network access, firewall as a service, and centralized management; database security, and endpoint and extended detection and response solutions; and data security solutions, such as web, network and endpoint data loss prevention, and encryption. The company also provides application security solutions comprising secure sockets layer visibility, web application firewall, application monitoring, and cyber security rating/risk score; application programming interface gateway and security solutions; cloud security solutions, including cloud security posture management, cloud-native application protection platform, cloud access security broker, and cloud risk monitoring; security information and event management, and email security solutions; and identity and access management, privileged identity management, privileged access management, and customer identity and access management solutions. In addition, it offers network and perimeter security solutions, such as firewall, intrusion prevention system, distributed denial of service, and domain name system security; web security, and integrating information technology (IT) and operational technology security solutions; and consulting, implementation, annual maintenance, sustenance, professional, and managed security services. The company operates a training centre; and distributes cybersecurity software products. It serves banking, capital market, NBFC, IT/information technology-enabled services, cybersecurity, automobile, insurance, pharmaceutical, FMCG, real estate, manufacturing, and other conglomerates industries. Meta Infotech Limited was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}